Coppell et al. v. Phillipson. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. July 18, 1890.) Appeal from circuit court, New York county.

Argued before Van Bkunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

Lewis Sanders, for appellant. G. L. Hives, for respondents. Brady, J.

This case is controlled by the case of Coppell v. Phillipson, ante, 901, (decided herewith.) The judgment must he affirmed, with costs. All concur.
